(309, 13, 5, 1, 'FIFA 21 Standard Edition Microsoft Xbox One Game', '16084551941. fifa-xbox-1-500x500.jpg', 0, 'FIFA 21 Standard Edition Microsoft Xbox One Game', '[{\"group_name\":\"Xbox Games\",\"brand_name\":\"Frostbite Technology\"}]', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 'Win as a team at EA SPORTS FIFA 21, powered by Frostbite technology. Whether on the streets or in the stadium, FIFA 21 has more ways to play than ever before - including the UEFA Champions League and CONMEBOL Libertadores. Create more goal opportunities than ever before with all-new dynamic attack systems in the smartest FIFA gameplay ever created. Manage every moment in Career Mode with new features that create more depth in matches, transfers and training, giving you more control over your team\'s rise to the top and making it easier than ever before to start your management career. More ways to play. More customization. More locations. Live the energy of the streets with your friends while showing your style in various cages and fields around the world with various styles of street football. Enjoy new ways to play FIFA\'s most popular mode while creating the dream team with old and new players on FIFA 21 Ultimate Team. Play with unparalleled authenticity in FIFA 21 with over 17,000 players and more than 700 teams along with 90 stadiums and more than 30 leagues offering the most realistic gaming experience.', 'no', 5200, 5200, 300, 1, 'in', 'no', '1608455194'),
(310, 13, 5, 1, 'Forza Horizon 4 Microsoft Xbox One Game', '16084563662. forza-horizon-500x500.jpg', 0, 'Forza Horizon 4 Microsoft Xbox One Game', '[{\"group_name\":\"Xbox Games\",\"brand_name\":\"Playground Games\"}]', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 'For the first time in the racing and driving genre, experience dynamic seasons in a shared open-world. Explore beautiful scenery, collect over 450 cars, and become a Horizon Superstar in historic Britain. Enjoy the largest and most diverse Horizon car roster yet, including over 100 licensed manufacturers. In the new open-ended campaign, everything you do progresses your game. Real players populate your world. When time of day, weather and seasons change, everyone playing the game experiences it at the same time. This is Britain Like Youâ€™ve Never Seen it. Discover lakes, valleys, castles, and breathtaking scenery all in spectacular native 4K and HDR on Xbox One X. Dynamic seasons change everything at the worldâ€™s greatest automotive festival. Go it alone or team up with others to explore beautiful and historic Britain in a shared open world. Collect, modify and drive over 450 cars. Race, stunt, create and explore â€“ choose your own path to become a Horizon Superstar.', 'no', 4200, 4200, 305, 1, 'in', 'no', '1608456366'),
