(662, 34, 9, 3, 'Smart Tilting TV Wall Mount Bracket for Most 32 36 40 42 Inch', '16112056361. Annotation 2021-01-04 105202.png', 97, 'Smart Tilting TV Wall Mount Bracket for Most 32 36 40 42 Inch', '', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 'UNIVERSAL DESIGN: Tilting TV wall mount for 14\" - 42\" flat-panel TVs up to 55lbs / 25 kg. Our TV tilt mount has a compatible faceplate that fits VESA 75X75mm (3\"x3\") 100X75mm (4â€x3â€) 100X100mm (4\"x4\") 200X100mm (8\"x4\") 200X200mm (8\"x8\"). Please check VESA (TV mounting hole pattern), TV weight, wall stud location and possible blocked cable/input.\r\nSAFE TO USE: High quality steel construction ensures safety. This wall mount TV bracket has high standards. It has been tested to hold 4 times the weight they\'re rated to based on UL standard so you can rest ured that it will hold the weight of your TV. It also comes with a locking mechanism with quick release which easily secures your TV to the wall.\r\nEASY INSTALLATION: Hang your television like a pro! Easy to install on 8 inch wood studs with standard harare. Get rid of the irritating glare from your screen and conveniently tilt your TV up to 15 degrees forwards or backwards as well as the ability to shift your baby laterally for perfect centering on your wall.\r\nSAVE SPACE: Keep your TV close to the wall to save space. Our low profile tilting mount holds the back of the TV just 1.3\" away from the wall for a sleek and tidy appearance.\r\nPerfect for single wood stud or brick/concrete mounting. All necessary mounting harare and instructions Manual included, Note: the TV screw sets provided are of standard size(M8/8mm screw not included) . They will fit the majority of TVs on the market. Should your TV require a different sized screw; the size can be established through the TV User Manual and can then be purchased from your local harare store. Please reach out to us if you have any problems at all.\r\nThe tilting wall mount is suitable for 14\" - 42\" flat-panel TVs. Its tilting system makes it easier to adjust the viewing angle. The design ensures TV mounting stability and security. Adjustable TV brackets offer lateral shift movement to allow perfect TV position, even with off-center wall wood studs. TV is positioned just 1.3\" / 32 mm from the wall for a clean, low-profile appearance. Comes with a harare bag, to save you time and money!\r\nDescription:\r\nPlease check whether the mount is suitable for your TV:\r\nFirst, please check your wall for wood studs. Our mount can also be used on concrete walls, and concrete anchors are included.But It can\'t be used on drywall.\r\nNext, the weight of your TV should be less than 55lbs (25kg).\r\nFinally, look at the back of your TV. Find the mounting holes and measure the horizontal and vertical distance. If the horizontal distance is within 8\" and the vertical distance is within 8\", then the bracket will work perfectly for you.\r\nSpecifications:\r\nFits 14\" to 42\" flat panel TVs.\r\nSupports TV weight up to 55 lbs (25kg).\r\nWall mount studs distance up to 8\".\r\nLow-profile design mounts your TV just 1.3\" from the wall.\r\nTilts up to 15 degrees for an optimal viewing experience.\r\nVESA Mounting Standard: 75 x 75mm, 100 x 75mm, 100 x 100mm, 200 x 100mm, 200 x 200mm.\r\nFeatures:\r\nWell eneered structure made with Less Metal - Green design makes the mount sturdy and stronger with less metal. The design ensures TV mounting stability and security.\r\nConvenient quick-release tabs design which you can easily pull down to unlock the TV from the wall plate.\r\nHorizontal movement adjustment for perfect TV positioning.\r\nPackage Contents:\r\n1x TV wall mount\r\n1x Standard mounting harare\r\n1x User manual', 'no', 2111, 2111, 500, 1, 'in', 'no', '1611205636'),
