(3127, 0, 22, 6, 'Fairy', '16121191503. Annotation 2021-01-17 123822.png', NULL, 'Hiking Bag', '', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 'Rip resistant and water repellent nylon backpack, lightweight and long-lasting.(only 0.9lb),\r\n40L large capacity with several pockets for storage and organization.\r\nAdjustable mesh shoulder straps and flexible sternum strap, distribute weight effectively and provide comfort and breathability.\r\nFold the backpack into its own pocket for easy storage.\r\nAdjustable buckle straps around the bag make the large backpack to be more compact size to carry.\r\nReflective strips around the backpack are more safer when you riding or running at night.', 'no', 1633, 1633, 500, 1, 'in', 'yes', '1612119150'),
(3128, 94, 22, 6, 'Pioneer Waterproof Military Tactical Backpack', '16121191864. Annotation 2021-01-17 123822.png', 0, 'Pioneer Waterproof Military Tactical Backpack', '[{\"group_name\":\"Hiking Bag\",\"brand_name\":\"ETOP\"}]', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 'Item Type: Backpacks,\r\nBackpack Usage: Normal Camping & Hiking,\r\nGender: Unisex,\r\nClosure Type: Zipper,\r\nCapacity: 30L,\r\nMaterial: 600D Nylon,\r\nDimension: 43x 25x 22cm/16.93x 9.84x 8.66 inch(Approx),\r\nPackage Content:1 X Camping Backpack.\r\n', 'no', 2657, 2657, 500, 1, 'in', 'yes', '1612119186'),
(3129, 94, 22, 6, '65L Hiking Backpack Waterproof ', '16121192515. Annotation 2021-01-17 123822.png', 0, '65L Hiking Backpack Waterproof ', '[{\"group_name\":\"Hiking Bag\",\"brand_name\":\"Best Life\"}]', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 'Extreme Durability: Made with high-quality nylon fabric that is water-resistant and abrasion-resistant, the backpack is built to last long and carry more load on your trips.\r\n65L Large Capacity: Includes main Pocket, top Pocket, side Pockets, front Pocket, waist Pockets, bottom Pocket, and exterior attachment straps, spacious enough for your trip.\r\nBreathable: Mesh back panels provide great airflow to keep your back cool and dry while also easing burden on your back.\r\nAdjust-able Straps: Adjust able shoulder, chest, waist straps to ensure a perfect, custom fit for men and women, which help evenly distribute the weight.\r\nSuitable for camping, hiking, climbing, traveling, and other outdoor activities.\r\n', 'no', 3015, 3015, 500, 1, 'in', 'no', '1612119251'),
(3130, 94, 22, 6, '6L Multifunctional Tactical Waist Bag', '16121192946. Annotation 2021-01-17 123822.png', 0, '6L Multifunctional Tactical Waist Bag', '[{\"group_name\":\"Hiking Bag\",\"brand_name\":\"NiceStore\"}]', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 'Durable material: made of water resistant oxford cloth and nylon material, wear resistant and scratch resistant,\r\n6L large capacity backpack: a spacious main compartment with zipping around closure, interior mesh pocket, two side pockets and front pocket,\r\nMultifunctional and detachable backpack: with the detachable shoulder strap, can be used as a shoulder bag, handbag or waist bag, multifunctional and practical,\r\nMole system: with the mole system on the front and back of the bag, can hang some water bottles and other attachment bags, with the buckles, durable and stable,\r\nMulti-purpose: suitable for all seasons, can be used as 3 days assault pack, bug-out bag, combat backpack, hunting backpack, survival backpack, military army rucksack, hiking rucksack or trekking backpack,\r\nApplication Position: Hand, Shoulder, Waist.', 'no', 826, 826, 500, 1, 'in', 'yes', '1612119294'),
